  "format": "lake",
  "body": "> 当两个元素是兄弟关系的时候，如果给上方元素设置`margin-bottom` 给下方元素设置`margin-top`，外边距会合并，最终外边距是这两个值中较大的那一个；\n\n\n> 当两个元素是父子关系的时候，如果给内部元素设置`margin-top`，则父元素也会随着向下移动；解决方式：给父元素添加`over-flow:hidden`\n\n",
  "body_draft": "",
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-undefined=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B2%2C1%5D%2C%5B2%2C1%5D%5D%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><blockquote style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); opacity: 0.6;\"><p data-lake-id=\"6684fe1c8ccad8bd461602e4fe94eefc_p_5\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">当两个元素是兄弟关系的时候，如果给上方元素设置<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">margin-bottom</code> 给下方元素设置<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">margin-top</code>，外边距会合并，最终外边距是这两个值中较大的那一个；</p></blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"f23fb9c519ff30bfe03d0b2cc2cac85d_p_6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><blockquote style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); opacity: 0.6;\"><p data-lake-id=\"0366241555a368f8f23cf41cc547d03c_p_7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">当两个元素是父子关系的时候，如果给内部元素设置<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">margin-top</code>，则父元素也会随着向下移动；解决方式：给父元素添加<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">over-flow:hidden</code></p></blockquote></div>",
  "body_lake": "<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"traditional\" /><blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"6684fe1c8ccad8bd461602e4fe94eefc_p_5\">当两个元素是兄弟关系的时候，如果给上方元素设置<code>margin-bottom</code> 给下方元素设置<code>margin-top</code>，外边距会合并，最终外边距是这两个值中较大的那一个；</p></blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"f23fb9c519ff30bfe03d0b2cc2cac85d_p_6\"><br /></p><blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"0366241555a368f8f23cf41cc547d03c_p_7\">当两个元素是父子关系的时候，如果给内部元素设置<code>margin-top</code>，则父元素也会随着向下移动；解决方式：给父元素添加<code>over-flow:hidden</code></p></blockquote>",
